{"id":31115,"date":"2024-01-27T23:30:20","date_gmt":"2022-01-27T18:00:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=31115"},"modified":"2022-11-29T17:10:30","modified_gmt":"2022-11-29T11:40:30","slug":"modern-bathroom-accessories","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/modern-bathroom-accessories\/","title":{"rendered":"Set Up Your New Bathroom With This Modern Bathroom Accessories List"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>When you&#8217;re setting up a new bathroom, there are the usual suspects like showerheads, sink and faucets. The bathroom fittings and sanitary ware are the obvious instalments that will be made when the bathroom is being built. But you can go a step further with modern bathroom accessories to give your bathroom a neat and orderly look. If you like being prepared before starting any project, you will like our modern bathroom accessories list. Here you will find all the items you need to consider when you&#8217;re setting up your new bathroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #1: Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A bathroom is of course incomplete without a mirror. It is most commonly installed above the sink which also makes up the vanity area of the bathroom. When you go shopping for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-mirror-design-ideas\/\">bathroom mirrors designs<\/a>, you will find a huge variety available in the market. There are bathroom mirrors in all shapes, sizes and designs, with and without frames. You can pick the one that best matches your preferences and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom interiors<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom accessories where the mirror is essential for every bathroom\" data-id=\"31118\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31118\" class=\"wp-image-31118\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222104\/modern-bathroom-accessories-where-the-mirror-is-essential-for-every-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A mirror is essential for every bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #2: Hooks And Holders<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The next most important item on the modern bathroom accessories list is hooks and holders. The hooks make it easy to hold up clothes, bathrobes and towels. Hooks are most commonly installed behind the bathroom door but you can also get them fixed on the wall. You can go for a single hook or a rail with multiple hooks. A horizontal rod, rack or ring holders are great options too. Ring holders are particularly handy for hanging hand towels near the sink.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience.jpg\" alt=\"modern bathroom accessories add hooks and holders for convenience\" data-id=\"31119\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31119\" class=\"wp-image-31119\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222502\/modern-bathroom-accessories-add-hooks-and-holders-for-convenience-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Add hooks and holders for convenience<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #3: Toilet Paper Holder<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The toilet paper holder \u2013 you guessed it \u2013 will go next to the toilet bowl. Remember not to skimp on this bathroom accessory. A toilet paper holder makes it easy to access and conveniently draw toilet paper. It&#8217;s better than having the toilet paper roll wander around the bathroom. You will also find a toilet paper holder with a lid option in the market which keeps the paper dry and in place.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom accessories with toilet paper holder which is an a important accessory for modern bathrooms\" data-id=\"31120\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31120\" class=\"wp-image-31120\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27222750\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-toilet-pape-holder-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">An important accessory for modern bathrooms<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #4: Shower Curtain<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a large bathroom, you may want to consider getting a shower curtain. It prevents water from spraying all over the bathroom and helps to keep the rest of the area dry. You will need to install a shower curtain rod in the area you want to enclose with a shower curtain. A shower curtain is an easier alternative to a glass door within the bathroom which is a more permanent change.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom accessories where you can pick from a range of shower curtain designs\" data-id=\"31122\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31122\" class=\"wp-image-31122\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223115\/Modern-bathroom-accessories-with-shower-curtain-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">You can pick from a range of shower curtain designs<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #5: Dispensers And Trays<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The next must-have items on the modern bathroom accessories list are dispensers and trays. These are very handy for the various bath products you will keep in your bathroom. You can get modern bathroom accessories set. It will have matching dispensers for everything from hand and body soaps to shampoos and conditioners, and a holder for toothbrushes and pastes. If you&#8217;re using liquid soaps, you can transfer them to bottle dispensers. For bar soaps, you can use a tray.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom accessories with dispensers and trays where countertop accessories are a must for organising\" data-id=\"31126\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31126\" class=\"wp-image-31126\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223359\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-dispensers-and-trays-where-countertop-accessories-are-a-must-for-organising-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Countertop accessories are a must for organising<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bathroom Accessories #6: Storage Solutions<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you&#8217;re setting up your bathroom, you also have to think about storage. You can have cabinets or shelves under the sink. You can also install wall-mounted shelves. Mirrors with cabinets are another popular option for the bathroom. This way, you can ensure that your countertop is not messy. Only the daily-use items can remain on the countertop. Everything else like the new batch of products, cleaning supplies and fresh towels can be arranged in the storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom accessories with storage solutions to make place for storage to hold bath products\" data-id=\"31130\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31130\" class=\"wp-image-31130\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/27223756\/modern-bathroom-accessories-with-storage-solutions-to-make-place-for-storage-to-hold-bath-products-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Make place for storage to hold bath products<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>From hooks and holders to modern <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-countertops-ideas\/\">bathroom countertop<\/a> accessories and modern bathroom accessories set \u2013 this list has all the things you will need when you&#8217;re setting up a new bathroom. These are all the essentials you will need for your bathroom. We make it easy for you to plan so that you don&#8217;t forget any of the must-haves. Remember to bookmark this bathroom accessories list for your reference.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about modern bathroom accessories, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/modern-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">modern bathroom design ideas<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Design your personal oasis of comfort<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=